phone 可唔可以理解為忠誠度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T01:16:36.000Z","msg":"忠誠不足<br />\n但android講忠誠度簡直笑話<br />\n窮同唔捨得俾錢又或者用慣先係主因<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99e26d213a699210317280676af54a49b354626","tid":1000361,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T01:52:20.000Z","msg":"Android系統忠誠度係高<br />\n<br />\n不過android品牌忠誠度低呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90bffe46e4cba3d07709dfb14e2ebf55f6601f5","tid":1000361,"uid":194130,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f06b49a2fddf271d682efec705e63cbb46b59310","tid":1000361,"uid":168911,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T12:31:10.000Z","msg":"大家諗下Android忠誠度係咩意思...<br />\n十九幾個brand...個個experience都唔同"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T02:53:07.000Z","msg":"Android忠誠度其實只係睇清事實<br />\n唔會再用冇教主既APPLE"},{"pid":"49e45c68c4bcefa3fd49a5de40f605d4f5171010","tid":1000361,"uid":144867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:23:03.000Z","msg":"其實成日互屌有乜謂？<br />\n<br />\n唔想煩， 要樣樣野都幾好， 咪俾貴啲買iphone囉&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nAndroid 就variety大啲，各有擅長，自己著重乜咪買乜機囉。"},{"pid":"753755783318494feb98f37ba73186c09d80c452","tid":1000361,"uid":208070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T04:47:37.000Z","msg":"米国電訊商補貼狂，100USD  1 部non - Chinese entry level phone <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}